  "detailed_description": "<h1>Features</h1><p>• <strong>Making Masterpieces:</strong> Paint, sketch, and retouch your artwork to complete your masterpiece and your memories<br>• <strong>Intricate Immersion:</strong> Dive into and explore panoramic, VR worlds inspired by Miyazaki/Studio Ghibli visuals<br>• <strong>Submerge in the Memory:</strong> Experience an evocative story, through the eyes of a passionate artist</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/d7b1b3f5d91e954ac15ad8b1df2be409.poster.avif?t=1770048466\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/d7b1b3f5d91e954ac15ad8b1df2be409.webm?t=1770048466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/d7b1b3f5d91e954ac15ad8b1df2be409.mp4?t=1770048466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Behind the Frame is a vivid, interactive fiction about an aspiring artist on the cusp of finishing the final piece of her gallery submission. Now available in VR, you'll be able to paint brushstrokes in a fully realized 3D space!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/00f4e8e61e0a38137fb7e8b4a87cbcbb.poster.avif?t=1770048466\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/00f4e8e61e0a38137fb7e8b4a87cbcbb.webm?t=1770048466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/00f4e8e61e0a38137fb7e8b4a87cbcbb.mp4?t=1770048466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A relaxing, eloquent experience that can be played at any pace. Become immersed in a panoramic world filled with resplendent colors, beautiful hand-animated visuals, and a smooth, easy-listening soundtrack. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/7095c3c624400864dbf5f2667c2d1296.poster.avif?t=1770048466\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/7095c3c624400864dbf5f2667c2d1296.webm?t=1770048466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/7095c3c624400864dbf5f2667c2d1296.mp4?t=1770048466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As a passionate artist, seek the missing colors that will bring your paintings to life - all while remembering to take the occasional coffee and breakfast breaks that keep you going. There is more than what meets the eye, for every painting has a story to tell.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/af5f60182720035d37cfc6eaf10d2be4.poster.avif?t=1770048466\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/af5f60182720035d37cfc6eaf10d2be4.webm?t=1770048466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/af5f60182720035d37cfc6eaf10d2be4.mp4?t=1770048466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
